A video of Lance O Leary kicking an elderly man s vehicle after a minor bumper bash, is currently making the rounds on social media, Alex News reports.The incident occurred on London Road which runs through Alexandra in Johannesburg.The video posted by Intelligence Bureau SA, shows a Porsche driver acting irrationally, trying to attack an elderly man in a Range Rover. The Porsche driver is also seen swearing and threatening the man before he furiously drives off.It is alleged O Leary will issue a full statement in due time.It is also believed he is an employee of SA Auto Supplies. Caxton News ServiceRead original story on